com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc
Class IDataDocument

java.lang.Object
  com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc.IDataRecord
      com.wm.adapter.sap.idoc.IDataDocument
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocument, com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocRecord, IDocConstants, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, java.io.Serializable
public class IDataDocument
extends IDataRecord
implements com.sap.conn.idoc.IDocDocument, com.wm.util.coder.IDataCodable, IDocConstants

Class that represents an IDoc using IData to implement the IDocDocument interface.

The document primarily holds the control record information of an IDoc. Furthermore it is the starting point for navigating through the contained segments providing the root segment as entry point.

Note, that the IDataDocument implementation works without meta data and therefore cannot check values for correctness when setting data in header fields.
